Path: This week in Nu #7
Content:
The first of the big refactors landed this week, with lots of work still in-progress.
wycats landed a major rewrite of the parser to better handle external/internal as well as more accurate coloring (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/728] #728
)
twe4ked and chhetripradeep added docs (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/802] #802
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/797] #797
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/795] #795
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/794] #794
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/793] #793
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/792] #792
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/791] #791
)
daveremy for helping out with the contributor book (
[link: https://github.com/nushell/contributor-book/pull/4] #4
)
Thanks to pizzafox, empath75, t-hart, ArekMiszcz, jordelver, daveremy, and jankeromnes for filing issues
